        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7604_p1"> <note type="com" xml:id="K_7604_c0">Nachträglicher Stempel oben rechts mit von dritter Hand eingetragener Nummer: <orig>Gotthardbahn | <date when="1877-11-05">5 <choice><abbr>NOV.</abbr><expan>NOVEMBER</expan></choice> 1877</date>. | <choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice> 4687.</orig> – 
              Nachträgliche Inhaltsangabe oben links von dritter Hand: <orig>Bewerbung für Uebernahme von Bauarbeiten. | I <choice><abbr>Depart.</abbr><expan>Departement</expan></choice> </orig> – 
              Nachträgliche Notiz unten links von dritter Hand: <orig><choice><abbr>Prot.</abbr><expan>Protokoll</expan></choice> <date when="1877-11-02">2. XI. 77</date>. <choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> 2356.</orig> </note> <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <hi rend="printed">IMPRESA COSTRUZIONI</hi>
          <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>
          <hi rend="printed">GUARNIERI, LORI &amp; <choice><abbr>C.</abbr><expan>Compagnia / Compagnie / Company (Gesellschaft)</expan></choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/><placeName key="Avellino (I)">AVELLINO</placeName> </hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7604_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>
          <placeName key="Florenz (I)">Firenze</placeName>
          <choice><abbr>A</abbr><expan>(Abkürzung nicht aufgelöst)</expan></choice> di <date when="1877-10-29">29 <add type="?"><choice><abbr>8bre</abbr><expan>ottobre (Oktober)</expan></choice> </add> 1877</date> </p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7604_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
          <choice><abbr>Illum. Sig:</abbr><expan>Illustrissimo Signore (verehrtester Herr)</expan></choice> A: Escher Presidente, 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>e componenti la Direzione della
        <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>Società delle Ferrovie del Gottardo
        <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/><placeName key="Luzern (Stadt)">Lucerna</placeName> </p>
      </div>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7604_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>L'Impresa Guarnieri, 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>Lori, e <choice><abbr>C:</abbr><expan>Compagnia / Compagnie / Company (Gesellschaft)</expan></choice> domiciliati in <placeName key="Florenz (I)">Firenze</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>Via Paolo Toscanelli <choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice> 1</p>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7604_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>Essendo a Sua notizia come cotesta
        <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>onorevole Direzione abbia da appaltare al<lb xml:id="p1-l14" break="no"/>cune costruzioni di Ferrovia, fa Istanza
            <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>alle <choice><abbr>SS: VV: Illume</abbr><expan>Signorie Vostre Illustrissime (Eure Hochwohlgeborenen)</expan></choice><note type="transcript">von IB nachträglich geändert, 16.07.2014</note> acciocché <add type="?">vogli<add>o</add>no</add> de<lb xml:id="p1-l16" break="no"/>gnarsi di ammettergli nel numero dei 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>concorrenti, trovandosi in questo momen<lb xml:id="p1-l18" break="no"/>mento in grado di assumere impegni per ave<lb xml:id="p1-l19" break="no"/>re quasi terminati i suoi Lavori e quin<lb xml:id="p1-l20" break="no"/>di a disposizione il proprio impianto.</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7604_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>Con la sperranza di essere onorati di una 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>sua replica, passano con sincero respetto 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>a sottoscriversi</p>
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7604_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>Delle <choice><abbr>SS: VV: Illume</abbr><expan>Signorie Vostre Illustrissime (Eure Hochwohlgeborenen)</expan></choice><note type="transcript">von IB nachträglich geändert, 16.07.2014</note> <choice><abbr>H</abbr><expan>Hoch</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Servi</abbr><expan>Servitore (Diener)</expan></choice> des:</p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7604_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l25"/><persName key="Guarnieri Ranieri">Ranieri Guarnieri</persName>
            <lb xml:id="p1-l26"/><persName key="Lori Olinto">Olinto Lori</persName> </p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>